    dc:creator "Freitag, Hendrik; Jäch, Manfred A." ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the species of Hydraena Kugelann (Coleoptera: Hydraenidae) from Palawan and Busuanga, with descriptions of eleven new species, and redescription of Hydraena (Hydraenopsis) scabra d’Orchymont, 1925" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175793>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175807>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175808> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175793>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Hydraena scabra d’Orchymont. a – c) aedeagus (specimen from Taytay, Palawan) in ventral, dorsal (parameral setae omitted) and lateral view (setae of left paramere omitted); d) male sternite X and spiculum; e) gonocoxite; f – g) spermatheca; h) female tergite X." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/175793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175807>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Geographical distribution of Hydraena scabra d’Orchymont; including one record from Mindanao (white circle) by Yano et al. 1983 (material not studied)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/175807/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.175808>
    dc:description "FIGURE 30. Collecting sites and geographical distribution of Hydraena species in Palawan and Busuanga, including enlarged map of St. Paul National Park: Hydraena scabra d’Orchymont, H. jojoorculloi sp. n., H. nielshaggei sp. n., H. zetteli sp. n., H. castanescens sp. n., H. claudia sp. n., H. kodadai sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/175808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

